crumble
------------------------------------------
Exploration of controlled loss of quality values for compressing CRAM files

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libhts3-1.23.1-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libhts-devel-1.23.1-1bl1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jkbonfield/crumble

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jkbonfield/crumble/archive/refs/tags/v0.9.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack crumble-0.9.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./crumble-0.9.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/crumble-0.9.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/crumble-0.9.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(crumble)
  /usr/bin/crumble.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/crumble.README
  /usr/share/doc/crumble/LICENSE.md
  /usr/share/doc/crumble/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/crumble.1.gz

